{"tid":901931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁招搖？】少女後頸紋「雞」字 網民猜測背後動機","createTime":"2018-11-14T11:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T01:50:59.000Z","uid":153228,"like":379,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"147ea3790a63277a14001f81ae1b17af2a61ca6d","tid":901931,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/14/1/1d3e6ea328bd670dc70b246949687af3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F14%2F1%2F1d3e6ea328bd670dc70b246949687af3.jpg&h=688665fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著社會愈來愈開放，大眾對於紋身的接受程度也愈來愈高，不再以紋身將人標籤為壞分子，亦有不少人會將一些個人訊息透過紋身告訴他人，不過在自己的後頸位置紋上一個中文「雞」字又是甚麼玩法呢？<br />\n<br />\n日前網上流傳一張沙女背影的相片，相中少女穿上米色上衣和白色短褲，露出雙腿，不過更為吸引他人眼球的卻是她後頸的紋身，可見她於後頸位置清楚紋上一個中文「雞」字，不禁令人嘖嘖稱奇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/11/14/f/f16fd2e75b72e7337be8b96f021eedbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F11%2F14%2Ff%2Ff16fd2e75b72e7337be8b96f021eedbb.jpg&h=29d9db11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信不少人都知道在廣東文化中，有人會以「雞」稱呼「妓女」，所以這位少女身上的紋身非常耐人尋味，有網民笑言這位少女可能正是想透過這個紋身作宣傳找生意。"},{"pid":"243e910bdf734f65ae79c0da4cfc806aac4408fb","tid":901931,"uid":12628,"like":621,"dislike":1,"score":620,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T11:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QudrZ0i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQudrZ0i.png&h=f745883c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5b3d4a22466805e2d3cba7b8a40f7112dbdd32c","tid":901931,"uid":34927,"like":273,"dislike":2,"score":271,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"諗起之前要求ptgf要打烙印個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716c79e5ec285d551dbbba3b8e6f710eaf587067","tid":901931,"uid":4942,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":